{
  "stem": "15694.12",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in contrast to the one tear which I had at the time when my father died, I had a stream of tears and convulsions.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I didn't know where they came from.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole thing broke-- the whole-- everything that you could think or not think of the brain can't take as much came on to me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the only thing I said to myself, alone, probably telling myself that I am alone.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And perhaps that was one of the times when I really had given up because it only-- it was so bad already that, you know-- my surroundings-- that even if anybody would be alive, it would be a miracle.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And the others-- the others died away like flies anyway.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I had a feeling I had to share-- oh, if I only had my father to share with him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wanted to share with someone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I looked at my bedmate, the only one left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The others had died.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he was dead as well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The next thing-- the Americans couldn't probably do what they wanted to do to feed us as quickly as they want to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but the war was over-- the, the, the, the, the camp-- there, I'm sure the SS had fled, as I say, a long time ago.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know who was in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't even know-- remember if we had eaten something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But some who could walk better-- I couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I just sort of step off the steps lightly.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I didn't go out of the barracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
